# Framework Routing

## When intent is unclear

Load **`using-compliance-agent-skills`** first.

## Routing table

| Signals | Primary skill | Preset |
| --- | --- | --- |
| ePHI, BAA, Security Rule | `hipaa-technical-safeguards` | `healthcare-hipaa` |
| Presidio, redaction pipeline | `hipaa-phi-redaction-pipeline` | `healthcare-hipaa` |
| LLM vendor BAA | `hipaa-baa-vendor-assessment` | `healthcare-hipaa` |
| Checkout scripts, Req 6.4.3 | `pci-dss-script-audit` | `fintech-pci-dss` |
| CDE, firewall, segmentation | `pci-dss-network-segmentation` | `fintech-pci-dss` |
| TSC mapping, SOC 2 scope | `soc2-trust-services-criteria` | `saas-soc2-type2` |
| Evidence binder | `soc2-evidence-collection` | `saas-soc2-type2` |
| CCM, drift dashboards | `soc2-ccm-continuous-monitoring` | `saas-soc2-type2` |
| IAM, MFA, RBAC | `access-control-identity-audit` | any |
| Logs, SIEM, Req 10 | `audit-logging-integrity` | any |
| Breach, incident | `breach-incident-response` | `healthcare-hipaa` |
| Vendor SOC reports | `vendor-third-party-risk` | any |
| OPA, Terraform, CI gates | `compliance-as-code-governance` | cloud presets |
| MCP OAuth, tool scope | `mcp-compliance-integration` | `regulated-ai-agents` |

## Cloud presets

AWS / Azure / GCP presets add cloud-specific control mappings — combine with framework skills.

## One primary skill per thread

Add secondary skills only when scope requires (see routing matrix in `using-compliance-agent-skills`).
